{"tid":2149040,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黃大仙男子大廈梯間吊頸亡","createTime":"2020-08-10T08:02:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T12:55:57.000Z","uid":240362,"like":12,"dislike":233,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"4c68ab2d41dda7f99a49e9ba03d12263e25ba71a","tid":2149040,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:02:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200810/B5BCKQVYRIURYMSMAR4VH27PJI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200810%2FB5BCKQVYRIURYMSMAR4VH27PJI%2F&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mADrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=daad818e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200810%2FB5BCKQVYRIURYMSMAR4VH27PJI%2F&h=dd79c647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200810/B5BCKQVYRIURYMSMAR4VH27PJI/</a><br />\n<br />\n竹園南邨富園樓，早上6時許，保安員巡邏至大廈3樓，赫然發現一名中年男子用USB電線吊頸，掛在梯間水管上昏迷不醒，於是報警，消防員到場協助解下，惟救護員證實男子已經死亡，警員封鎖現場展開調查。死者姓劉（58歲），警方初步調查相信事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。"},{"pid":"f453a1d49bc2a98b24e815b2b27b76cdc4af00fb","tid":2149040,"uid":132587,"like":203,"dislike":6,"score":197,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:03:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43707563cfa9295985a1782530764312c588d4dc","tid":2149040,"uid":11291,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:05:05.000Z","msg":"Usb線？"},{"pid":"ae5552e153dee586a6fd86686c7cbf079a6e6ab2","tid":2149040,"uid":43062,"like":94,"dislike":0,"score":94,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:06:10.000Z","msg":"乜撚野呀USB吊得起個人？"},{"pid":"cd5397eb0778324f9759e3ec8838318fc9de2701","tid":2149040,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:13:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc9475b8bf1d82e794006ed09ce166d6f904d591","tid":2149040,"uid":108337,"like":73,"dislike":1,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:14:32.000Z","msg":"得黑警先會用usb線殺人"},{"pid":"947ceb45832804ce60c41a55ca55ba9577e9934f","tid":2149040,"uid":256783,"like":36,"dislike":3,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:15:08.000Z","msg":"睇嚟又係之前死於非命嗰啲後生仔既屋企人 <br />\n<br />\nrip"},{"pid":"84d11d55ef686bc87c367ca0184d39624cf1a66d","tid":2149040,"uid":290118,"like":116,"dislike":0,"score":116,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:16:49.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">橋底色魔離奇獲電腦線警署上吊亡</span><br />\n<br />\n九龍灣姦劫案驚變自殺奇案，橋底色魔在警署羈留室自縊亡。姦劫案疑犯落網後，在秀茂坪警署扣查十八小時，昨晨被發現在羈留室用電腦線上吊自殺，送院不治。因姦劫案疑犯曾用電腦ＵＳＢ線綑綁女事主，令案件更添懸疑。警隊高層下令徹查真相，由西九龍總區重案組調查，循保安漏洞及人為疏忽方向，追查疑犯的自殺工具來源及如何帶入羈留室，不排除疑犯盜取警署電腦線，瞞過搜身警員帶入，期間亦因火警鐘大鳴轉換過羈留室，但都無人知他身藏電腦線及用來尋死，懷疑有警員「漏招」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170512/00174_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170512%2F00174_001.html&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mADrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=6d262024\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170512/00174_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n明啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f1be4ad0c2680933bd00bcbb2ea11b10cfd48c","tid":2149040,"uid":68111,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"84d11d55ef686bc87c367ca0184d39624cf1a66d","tid":2149040,"uid":290118,"like":116,"dislike":0,"score":116,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:16:49.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">橋底色魔離奇獲電腦線警署上吊亡</span><br />\n<br />\n九龍灣姦劫案驚變自殺奇案，橋底色魔在警署羈留室自縊亡。姦劫案疑犯落網後，在秀茂坪警署扣查十八小時，昨晨被發現在羈留室用電腦線上吊自殺，送院不治。因姦劫案疑犯曾用電腦ＵＳＢ線綑綁女事主，令案件更添懸疑。警隊高層下令徹查真相，由西九龍總區重案組調查，循保安漏洞及人為疏忽方向，追查疑犯的自殺工具來源及如何帶入羈留室，不排除疑犯盜取警署電腦線，瞞過搜身警員帶入，期間亦因火警鐘大鳴轉換過羈留室，但都無人知他身藏電腦線及用來尋死，懷疑有警員「漏招」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170512/00174_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170512%2F00174_001.html&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mADrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgL